{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_10_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 「そばにいる」",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "葵、『情熱だけで生きてみろ』の\nMVの撮影日程、メールで送ったけど確認したか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ about “Try Living on Passion Alone”—\nI sent you the MV shooting schedule by email. Did you check it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "確認してあるよ\nそれにしても、初披露からだいぶ時間が空いたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I checked it.\nStill‚ it’s been quite a while since we first performed it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 13.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』で曲を披露したのは\n随分前だよ。もっと早くやれば良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The time we performed it at “Grab the BIG4” was\nway back. We should’ve done this sooner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲はいつリリースするの、って\n会う人みんなに言われて困ってるんだけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ everyone I meet keeps asking me\nwhen we’ll release that song— it’s getting awkward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.666666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.766666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも『Grab the BIG4』で\nあの曲を披露する予定はなかったからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To begin with‚ during “Grab the BIG4”—\nWe didn’t even plan to perform that song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.266666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだっけ。んー、そうだったかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Hmm‚ yeah‚ maybe you’re right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 35.2999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だからMV撮影の準備なんてしてなかったんだよ\nそれにBIG4になってすぐ、海外ツアーに行っただろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why we hadn’t prepared for the MV shoot.\nAnd right after you became BIG4‚ you went on an overseas tour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "レコーディングだって、ついこの間済ませたばかりだ\nむしろ早かったと思ってほしいくらいだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ the recording was only finished recently.\nIf anything‚ I’d say that was actually pretty fast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。{user}君は、最速で撮影を\n組んでくれたんだね。じゃあ、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You arranged the shoot\nas quickly as possible‚ huh? Then‚ thank you for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.766666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ苦労はしたが、それが俺の仕事だからな\nところで、俺からも一つ、質問をいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It took some effort‚ but that’s my job.\nBy the way‚ can I ask you something‚ too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 65.6999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "何が聞きたいの？　僕が今ハマってる音ゲーとか？\n一つならいいよ。僕の質問に一つ答えてもらったからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you want to know? The rhythm game I’m into lately‚ maybe?\nI’ll allow one. You answered one of mine‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 75.166666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もっと大事なことだよ。その例の曲についてなんだが\n活動休止中に、葵が振り付けを作っていたよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s something more serious. It’s about that song.\nYou worked on the choreography during your hiatus‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、状況的に四人で合わせる時間なんてなかった\nどうして準決勝で、あんなに完璧に合わせられたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But given the situation‚ there was no time for the four of you to practice together.\nSo how were you able to perform it so perfectly in the semifinals?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 92.366666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや……そもそもあの勝負所で、どうして満足に\n練習も出来ていない、未発表の新曲をやったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or rather‚ why did you choose to perform\nan unreleased new song you hadn’t even fully practiced?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 100.2333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、あの時も同じようなことを聞かれたっけ\nというか、質問が二つある気がするんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it‚ someone asked me that back then‚ too.\nBy the way‚ that sounds like two questions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6013351094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "もしもインタビューなんかで急に話されでもしたら\n困るからな。さすがに把握しておきたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it suddenly came up in an interview or something‚\nthat’d be a problem. I need to be in the loop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.4333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 115.4333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になった直後は、慌ただしかったから\nなぁなぁにされたけど……今度こそ、話してもらうぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things were hectic right after you became BIG4‚\nwe let it slide back then… but this time‚ you’re telling me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ。大した話じゃないけど\nそんなに知りたいなら話すよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. It’s not that big a deal‚ though.\nBut if you want to know that badly‚ I’ll tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 128.6999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "あれは、『Grab the BIG4』\n決勝トーナメント開始の、少し前の話なんだけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was right before the “Grab the BIG4”‚\nfinal tournament was about to begin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 135.7166620891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ここで曲調が変わるから、フォーメーションも変えて\n……少し難しいステップだけど、みんななら出来るはず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The tone changes here‚ so the formation should shift too.\n…It’s a tricky step‚ but everyone will manage it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4999954224,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7633.333333299987,
          "startTime": 144.3999954224
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、葵\n……もしかして、新曲の振り付けを作ってるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice work‚ Aoi.\n…Are you working on the choreography for the new song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "うん。活動休止中とはいえ\n僕も一応まだ、リズノワのメンバーだからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Even if I’m on a break‚\nI’m still technically a member of LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "自分でやるって言い出したことなんだから、やらないと\nそれで{user}君は何しに来たの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was the one who said I’d do it‚ so I have to.\nSo what brings you here‚ {user}-kun?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.3999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "葵がリズノワの活動をしばらく休むって聞いたから\n心配して、様子を見に来たんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard you were taking a break from LizNoir—\nSo I came to check on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "そう。面倒見がいいね、{user}君は\nでも、僕のことは気にしないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You’re quite caring‚ aren’t you‚ {user}-kun?\nBut don’t worry about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.2333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワにとって大切な時に、こんな所にいる僕に\n時間をかける必要なんてない。それより……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s an important time for LizNoir‚ you don’t need to\nspend your time on me. More importantly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.4333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』の決勝トーナメントを\n控えてる、莉央達のそばにいてあげてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With the “Grab the BIG4” finals coming up—\nI want you to stay close to Rio and the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.7333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん達のこと、気にかけてるんだな\n大丈夫。三人のフォローはしっかりやるから任せてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really care about them‚ don’t you?\nDon’t worry‚ I’ll support the three of them properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.8666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、葵にだって助けは必要だ。莉央さん達と\n距離を取っている今の葵には、相談相手がいた方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Aoi‚ you need support too. Since you’re keeping\nsome distance from them‚ it’d be good to have someone to talk to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.6666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "僕に助けが……相談相手が必要？\nそう、なのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need… support? Someone to talk to?\nMaybe… you’re right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.9666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "俺はそう思ってる。今は相談ごとがないならそれでいい\nもし何か話したいことが出来たら、声を掛けてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what I think. If there’s nothing now‚ that’s fine.\nBut if you ever want to talk‚ come to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.1666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君は、お節介が過ぎるね\n……僕なんかに、そこまでするなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re too meddlesome‚ {user}-kun.\n…Going that far for someone like me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.5666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "次の仕事まではここにいる。明日も来る\nだから葵、黙っていなくなったりしないでほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be here until the next job. I’ll come again tomorrow.\nSo‚ Aoi‚ please don’t just disappear without saying anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.8999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。黙っていなくなったりはしない\n約束するよ。……ねぇ、{user}君",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright. I won’t vanish without a word.\nI promise. …Hey‚ {user}-kun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.8999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "……どうした？　何か言いたいことがあるなら\n溜め込まないで教えてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What is it? If there’s something you want to say—\nDon’t keep it in. Tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.1333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。大したことじゃ、ないんだ\nなんでもないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… it’s nothing important.\nIt’s nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.5666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 264.1666620891
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 264.1666620891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこともあったな。葵が活動を休止していた頃か\nところで、その話と俺の質問にどんな関係があるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yeah‚ that was back when you were on hiatus.\nBut what does that have to do with my question?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.1666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、言いそびれてたことを思い出してね\n僕のこと、気にかけてくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It reminded me of something I didn’t say back then.\nThank you for caring about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.7666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 284.5666295369
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "僕がスランプに陥って、でもその原因が分からなくて\n悩んでいた時、寄り添ってくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was in a slump‚ not even knowing why—\nYou stayed by me through it. Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.8666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あぁ……どういたしまして\nでも、俺が葵の悩みを解決した訳じゃないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Oh… you’re welcome.\nBut it’s not like I solved your problem or anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.5999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 302.1666295369
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "いいんだ。大事なのは、僕が弱っていたあの時\n「そばにいる」って君が声を掛けてくれたことだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s fine. What mattered was‚ when I was at my weakest—\nYou told me‚ “I’ll be by your side.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.8666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 310.6999628703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ、僕はそろそろ帰るよ。明日も仕事だからね\nそれが僕にはとても嬉しかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well then‚ I’ll head home. I’ve got work tomorrow.\nThat meant a lot to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.6999628703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 316.8333287557
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。少しでも、葵の役に立てたなら嬉しいよ\n……じゃなくて、ちょっと待て。俺の質問への答えは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I’m glad if I could help you even a little.\n…Wait‚ hold on. What about my question’s answer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 326.5463749077,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
